Fitch &amp; Shump (1979), Lausen et al. (2019), Nagorsen &amp; Brigham (1993), Parker et al. (1997), Simmons (2005), Wilson &amp; Ruff (1999), van Zyll de Jong (1985).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
